item.title: CVE-2024-5422|2024-06-04T08:06:45.294Z -- seh%20computertechnik -- utnserver%20pro
item.description: An uncontrolled resource consumption of file descriptors in SEH Computertechnik utnserver Pro, SEH Computertechnik utnserver ProMAX, SEH Computertechnik INU-100 allows DoS via HTTP.This issue affects utnserver Pro, utnserver ProMAX, INU-100 version 20.1.22 and below.
